feed.title: Aspire Biopharma's Wholly Owned Subsidiary, Buzz Bomb Caffeine Company, Partners with Blue Shark Beverages to Expand Southern California Distribution
feed.summary: Aspire Biopharma's subsidiary, Buzz Bomb Caffeine Company, has partnered with Blue Shark Beverages to expand the distribution of its BUZZ BOMB™ sublingual caffeine stick pack across Southern California. This strategic agreement, effective February 1, aims to leverage Blue Shark's established network to meet the growing demand for "better-for-you" energy products, starting with a rollout in Palm Springs and the Coachella Valley, including major festivals. BUZZ BOMB™ offers a fast-acting, portable caffeine solution in four flavors, targeting athletes, professionals, and individuals seeking an immediate energy boost without traditional sugary energy drinks.

feed.title: Textron System' Damocles Loitering Munition Selected For US Army LASSO Contract
feed.summary: Textron Systems has been awarded a prototype agreement by the U.S. Army for the Low Altitude Stalking & Strike Ordnance (LASSO) program. Under this agreement, Textron Systems will deliver and demonstrate its Damocles loitering munition system, which features an advanced GEN2 Explosively Formed Penetrator and is designed for decisive lethality in peer warfare environments. The Damocles system in this program is integrated with a VTOL uncrewed aircraft system to provide a top-attack capability without requiring launch or recovery equipment.

feed.title: DARPA Taps RTX to Advance Kilometer-Range X-ray Vision
feed.summary: RTX's BBN Technologies has been awarded a DARPA contract under its X-ray Extreme-range Non-imaging Analysis (XENA) program to develop kilometer-range X-ray imaging capabilities. This initiative aims to enhance situational awareness for service members by reconstructing hidden object geometries from a distance, providing critical insights when close access is not feasible. BBN will develop algorithms and software that use advanced mathematical modeling to interpret low-quality, long-range X-ray data to reveal detailed information about concealed objects and threats.

feed.title: Toaster-sized Earth-imaging satellite taps Ascent Solar on SpaceX ride
